title: TmsT's new Keen animation
content:
On one of my other geek forums, somebody (Redlof) posted photos of himself costumed as Commander Keen. It was so hilarious that I had to immediately make an animation using the photos (and arrange some music for it).

Here's the movie: [url=http://tmst.twu.net/flash/redlofkeen1.html]"I AM Commander Keen!"[/url] [img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-grin.gif[/img]

Don't get too excited, it only took me a couple of hours or so. [img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-embarrassed.gif[/img] ----------
The Chasm of Strife (deceased): www.ThisStrife.com/Sluggy/chasm.htm
